claim.claim-text:
A system for facilitating power tool operation, comprising:
a first camera;
a computing device receiving information from the first camera;
a display for displaying information received from the computing device; and
a reference marker having at least two markers viewable by the first camera, the reference marker being disposed on a power tool or separate from the power tool;

wherein the computing device calculates a position of the reference marker from the information received from the first camera.
